#: _includes/home.html:2
msgid ""
"Stellarium is a free open source planetarium for your computer. It shows a "
"realistic sky in 3D, just like what you see with the naked eye, binoculars "
"or a telescope."
msgstr ""
"Stellarium es un planetario gratuito de código abierto para su computadora. "
"Muestra un cielo realista en 3D, tal como se ve a simple vista, con "
"binoculares o con un telescopio."

#: _includes/home.html:9 _includes/home.html:12 _layouts/screenshots.html:12
msgid ""
"A shooting star flashes past the Jupiter. You can select different "
"intensities in the View window."
msgstr ""
"Una estrella fugaz parpadea detrás de Júpiter. Puede seleccionar diferentes "
"intensidades en la ventana Vista."

#: _includes/home.html:13 _includes/home.html:22 _includes/home.html:30
#: _includes/home.html:39 _includes/home.html:48
msgid "view screenshots"
msgstr "Ver capturas de pantalla"

#: _includes/home.html:18 _layouts/screenshots.html:17
msgid ""
"The great nebula in Orion. Press N to bring up the nebula labels. Also shown"
" are constellation lines, press C to show or hide them."
msgstr ""
"La gran nebulosa en Orión. Presione N para ver la etiqueta de las nebulosas."
" También se muestran las líneas de constelación. Presione C para activar o "
"desactivarlas."

#: _includes/home.html:21
msgid "The great nebula in Orion. Press N to bring up the nebula labels."
msgstr ""
"La gran Nebulosa de Orión. Presione N para ver las etiquetas de las "
"nebulosas."

#: _includes/home.html:26 _includes/home.html:29 _layouts/screenshots.html:16
msgid "The dance of the planets above ESO headquarters, near Munich."
msgstr "La danza de los planetas sobre la sede ESO, cerca de Munich."

#: _includes/home.html:35 _includes/home.html:38 _layouts/screenshots.html:11
msgid "Full sky view of the constellations, their boundaries, the Milky Way."
